				item: "waystones:waystone"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Waystones"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -4.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000005"]
			description: ["FTB Chunks lets you claim chunks so other players cannot build or break blocks inside them, and lets you force-load claimed chunks so they continue processing while you are offline. Open the chunk map with the FTB Chunks key (default: M), then click to claim the chunk under your cursor. Toggle force-load mode (the lightning bolt icon) on individual chunks to keep machines running. Force-loaded chunks have a per-player limit — use them only on machine rooms and active farms, not your entire base footprint. Claimed but not force-loaded chunks still prevent grief but pause machine processing when you log off."]
			id: "QL01000000000006"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000006"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [{
				id: "QL02000000000006"
				title: "Claim and Force-Load a Chunk"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "FTB Chunks"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -5.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000001"]
			description: ["Storage Drawers are the primary bulk item storage solution for ore, ingots, and high-volume commodities. Each Drawer block holds a configurable number of item types — Full 4-Drawer holds four distinct items; Full 2-Drawer holds two in larger stacks; Compacting Drawer automatically converts between nuggets, ingots, and blocks. Right-click to insert; Shift+Right-click to extract. Connect drawers to a Drawer Controller block and all connected drawers behave as a single searchable inventory accessible via Pipez or ME Storage Buses. Build a full wall of Full 4-Drawers before your GTCEu ore processing line goes live."]
			id: "QL01000000000007"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000007"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [
				{
					id: "QL02000000000007"
					item: "storagedrawers:oak_full_drawers_4"
					type: "item"
				}
				{
					id: "QL02000000000008"
					item: "storagedrawers:controller"
					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Storage Drawers"
			x: 3.0d
			y: -2.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000007"]
			description: ["Functional Storage upgrades the Drawer concept with higher-tier materials and configurable capacity. Drawers tier from Oak through Netherite; higher tiers hold exponentially more items per slot. The Functional Storage Controller links all Functional Storage drawers in the same network as a single unified inventory — connect via Drawer Link Cable. The Ender Drawer provides a cross-dimensional shared inventory that syncs with any other Ender Drawer using the same frequency color code, making it the primary method for transferring items between your base and Nether or dimensional outposts."]
			id: "QL01000000000008"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000008"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
				type: "item"
