					type: "item"
				}
			]
			title: "Sophisticated Storage"
			x: 3.0d
			y: -5.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000009"]
			description: ["Sophisticated Backpacks equip in the chest slot or Curios back slot and provide portable inventory expansion. Tier ladder: Basic → Iron → Gold → Diamond → Netherite, each adding more slots and upgrade card capacity. Upgrade cards include: Filter Upgrade (auto-picks up only specified items), Magnet Upgrade (pulls items from the ground into the pack), Smelting Upgrade (auto-smelts incoming raw ores), Compacting Upgrade (converts nuggets to ingots in real time), and Tank Upgrade (stores fluids). Equip a Diamond Backpack with Filter and Magnet before long Mine & Slash map runs — it cleans up the floor automatically and separates loot from junk without manual sorting."]
			id: "QL01000000000010"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000010"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [{
				id: "QL02000000000013"
				item: "sophisticatedbackpacks:backpack"
				type: "item"
			}]
			title: "Sophisticated Backpacks"
			x: 3.0d
			y: -7.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000001"]
			description: ["Inventory Sorter and Mouse Tweaks work together to reduce inventory management time. Inventory Sorter: middle-click any inventory slot to sort the entire container alphabetically; Shift+middle-click to sort by stack size. Mouse Tweaks: hold left-click and drag across empty slots to distribute the held stack evenly; hold right-click and drag to place one item per slot across a range; scroll the mouse wheel while hovering a slot to move items one at a time between the container and your inventory. These bindings work in every inventory in the pack — chest, furnace, GTCEu machine, backpack, and Drawer Controller. Learn them once and they apply everywhere."]
			id: "QL01000000000011"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000011"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [{
				id: "QL02000000000014"
				title: "Learn Middle-Click Sort"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "Inventory Management"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -7.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000001"]
			description: ["Pipez provides the simplest item, fluid, and energy pipe network in the pack. Place any pipe type adjacent to a container or machine — it connects automatically to any other Pipez pipe of the same type within range. Filter each pipe end by right-clicking it with an item to restrict what enters or exits that connection. Upgrade cards inserted into the pipe increase extraction speed and filter capacity. The Universal Pipe combines item, fluid, and energy transfer in one pipe block, which reduces wire and tube clutter significantly. Use Pipez as the primary routing layer between GTCEu machines and Drawer Controllers in your base."]
			id: "QL01000000000012"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000012"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
				type: "item"
			}]
			tasks: [
				{
