			title: "Create Jetpack"
			x: -3.0d
			y: -10.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000001"]
			description: ["Quark adds dozens of small improvements that activate silently in the background. Notable features: double-click any chest slot to sort the container contents; trowel-right-click with a stack to randomly place one of several block variants for natural-looking builds; shift-right-click a stack of arrows onto a bow to quick-load it; Variant Chests and Barrels carry the wood type of their material; Matrix Enchanting replaces the vanilla enchanting table with a table that shows all available enchantments and lets you select specific ones at higher material cost. All Quark features can be toggled individually in the Quark config. If something feels wrong, check if Quark changed it."]
			id: "QL01000000000018"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "QL03000000000018"
				item: "mmorpg:currency/mirror"
