			title: "Quark"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -9.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["QL01000000000018"]
			description: ["Supplementaries adds functional decorative blocks that serve real utility roles. Rope (place on any surface, extend down by placing more) lets you create climbable vertical descents without ladders — essential for deep mine shafts and cliff faces. Sign Posts display multiple directional labels at an intersection. Jars store single item types for display and easy retrieval. The Flute calls passive mobs to you. Rope Arrows attach rope to walls at range for remote installations. Supplementaries blocks blend into vanilla aesthetics and fill the gap between pure decorative mods and pure utility mods — they are practical objects that also look right in a built base."]
			id: "QL01000000000019"
			rewards: [{
